âœ… **Fixed badge colors** - Status badge shows RED for stress presence
âœ… **Fixed progress bars** - Progress bar shows RED for stress presence
âœ… **Added parameter awareness** - Color functions now check parameter type
âœ… **Updated all usages** - All color function calls pass parameter name
âœ… **Consistent logic** - 0/3 = healthy (green), 1-3/3 = unhealthy (red)

